)F    FUNCTION -

         THIS IS THE STARSHIP ENTERPRISE, ITS FIVE YEAR MISSION TO
      EXPLORE NEW WORLDS, NEW CIVILIZATIONS. TO GO WHERE NO MAN HAS
      GONE BEFORE.

         IN THIS GAME YOU ARE GIVEN A FINITE AMOUNT OF TIME TO
      DESTROY A FLEET OF KLINGONS. YOU ARE RATED BY THE AMOUNT
      OF TIME YOU TOOK AND THE NUMBER OF KLINGONS DESTROYED.

)X    SYNTAX

         STARTREK

)O    OPERANDS -

))CO     COMMANDS:

     SR = SHORT RANGE SENSOR SCAN
     LR = LONG RANGE SENSOR SCAN
     PH = FIRE PHASERS
     PT = FIRE PHOTON TORPEDOES
     DA = DAMAGE CONTROL REPORT
     DE = SELF-DESTRUCT
